title: MisterMusic Show 311 - indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show episode 311 [120 minutes] 192kbps MP3 Stereo -


On this week's MisterMusic Show, new tunes from Go Swim, Spoon,and Morrissey.
Plus a big hit in the US and UK from mid-July 1986 is the 'Oldie of the Week'. It was all over the radio that summer....if you're old enough to remember.

Plus the usual mix of indie,alternative and classic hits from more than 5 decades squeezed into 2 hours. Broadcasting weekly, and heard globally it's The MisterMusic Show.



The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
